by Windows:

1. In C:\temp>  create file: SumTwoNumbers.java
2. open SumTwoNumbers.java with notepad++ and write:

import java.util.Scanner;

public class SumTwoNumbers {
	public static void main(String[] args) {
		Scanner input = new Scanner(System.in);
		System.out.print("Input number a = ");
		int a = input.nextInt();
		System.out.print("Input number b = ");
		int b = input.nextInt();
		int sum = a + b;
		System.out.printf("The sum of: (%d + (%d)) = %d", a, b, sum);
	}
}

3. save file and open windows command prompt
4. C:\temp>javac SumTwoNumbers.java  -> create SumTwoNumbers.class
5. C:\temp>java SumTwoNumbers  -> execute program
